    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone looking for a functional daily driver. The exterior has seen some wear, including several noticeable scratches, paint fading on the hood, and a few small door dings. Inside, the upholstery shows signs of use with some minor staining and wear on the driver's seat, though all electronics and the air conditioning are still working correctly. Mechanically, it starts reliably and drives well, though it may require some routine maintenance soon, such as new brake pads or tires. It\u2019s not a show car, but it\u2019s a solid, honest vehicle that will get you where you need to go.",
      "price": 17500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! It has been well-loved and shows some honest wear and tear, but it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone needing reliable transportation. With a bit of TLC, this car still has plenty of miles left to give!",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
